{"tid":1236484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍自己友不如圍敵人","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:35:45.000Z","uid":263306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9c18d210e451a8a1934c67a6063553759dd984","tid":1236484,"uid":263306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"今日龍和道啲人挑起話民主派議員做唔到野，我聽到好唔開心，話晒大家都係自己人，無功都有勞，點解硬要人跟你哋的決定做事呢？<br />\n<br />\n朱迪叫大家諗下野，無錯，呢個時候是要發揮創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要圍自己友，點解唔去圍建制呀？之前大家話要比壓力佢哋，都無做到。<br />\n<br />\n還有以子之茅攻子之盾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係諗下，如果葉劉咁想做特首，我們比個機會佢拉林鄭下台，你又話得唔得呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5adac8a1e3307b1f581e82c7cdc9df9f92a5ee3","tid":1236484,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手一齊周圍post：<br />\n反送中Deadline、黑警、醫管局、所有被捕政治犯、撤回暴動定性。<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責。加油！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445cb0a44e4f9115fafa19b0b0def437c15d0d4a","tid":1236484,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手一齊周圍post：<br />\n反送中Deadline、黑警、醫管局、所有被捕政治犯、撤回暴動定性。<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責。加油！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=